ReportDocumentForm is a Form
    is primary
    title is "<FormTitle>"
    Layout
        single column
            Name
            create stamp
                display only
            Description
                display only
            MimeType
                display only
            SourceType
                display only
            visible when (UsesSourceKey1)
                SourceKey1
                    label is SourceKey1Label
                    display only
            visible when (UsesSourceKey2)
                SourceKey2
                    label is SourceKey2Label
                    display only
            visible when (UsesSourceKey3)
                SourceKey3
                    label is "KeyHash"
                    display only
            button of "View"
                visible when (HasDocument)
                view Document
